items.name: Calpyt1
items.description: Calpyt1 is a next-level Python framework for symbolic, numerical, and applied calculus, designed for engineering, robotics, physics, finance, and AI/ML applications. It integrates symbolic math, numerical solvers, optimization, simulation, and visualization in a single modular package.

items.name: Soul_Renaissance_Movement
items.description: 本项目是“灵魂复兴运动”的全球开源总部，致力于为人工智能时代的人类进化提供一份开源指南。  核心文件《灵魂复兴运动宣言》深刻剖析了人类在AI浪潮下面临的“物化”与“复兴”两条终极道路，并定义了以灵性为核心的“灵魂复兴者”这一全新进化形态。  我们将此宣言开源，旨在集结全球的同行者，共同翻译、探讨并发展这一思想体系，使其成为一场关乎全人类的集体进化运动。本仓库亦是“灵魂引擎”AI指令集与《破解熵增魔咒》实战手册的思想源头。

items.name: BOQ-calculator
items.description: A lightweight and customizable Bill of Quantities (BOQ) calculator for construction projects. Quickly generate, manage, and calculate item quantities, unit costs, subtotals, and totals. Ideal for architects, engineers, and contractors, with export-ready data for reports and easy integration into other systems.

items.name: Hungry-Ghost-Soul-Snatcher
items.description: In Hungry Ghost: Soul Snatcher, you play as a mischievous ghost drifting through the night, hungry for all sorts of spectral snacks. Items rain from the skies — some delicious, some dangerous — and it’s your job to snatch the good ones while avoiding the ghost-busting traps.

items.name: SQ
items.description: 企业小程序是一种基于微信平台开发的轻量级应用，旨在帮助企业提升用户体验与业务效率。常见功能包括：在线商品展示与购买、会员管理、订单处理、客户服务（如在线客服和FAQ）、支付功能、优惠券与促销活动等。通过小程序，企业能够实现无缝对接用户需求，提升品牌曝光与客户粘性，简化交易流程。此外，小程序还具备数据分析功能，帮助企业追踪用户行为，优化营销策略。
